{"id":"zalmonah","term":"Zalmonah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Shady, one of the stations of the Israelites in the wilderness (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:41\">Num. 33:41</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"Numbers 33:42\">42</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["Numbers 33:41","Numbers 33:42"]}